title: Cutter
content:
Y = 10
forwardToken = 0

function turnAround()
    turtle.turnLeft()
    turtle.turnLeft()
end

function forward2()
    turtle.forward()
    turtle.forward()
    forwardToken = forwardToken + 1
    print(forwardToken)
end

function digdown()
    tokenY = 0
    while tokenY < Y do
        turtle.digDown()
        turtle.down()
        tokenY = tokenY + 1
    end
end

function goBackUp()
    while tokenY ~= 1 do --it's 1 instead of 0 because of the up in replant
        turtle.up()
        tokenY = tokenY - 1
    end
end

function replant()
    turtle.up()
    turtle.placeDown()
end

function goBack()
    turnAround()
    forward2()
end

forward2()
forward2()
turtle.turnRight()
forward2()
digdown()
replant()
goBackUp()
goBack()

title: BoreTrainFront
content:
local modem = peripheral.wrap("right")

modem.open(25904)

while turtle.getFuelLevel() <= 0 do
	term.clear()
	term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
	print("Missing fuel in slot 1")
	turtle.select(1)
	turtle.refuel()

	os.sleep(0.5)
end

term.clear()
term.setCursorPos(1, 1)

print("Drone Train Front")

local aggregate = 25905

while true do
	local event, modemSide, channel, replyChannel, message, distance = os.pullEvent("modem_message")
    
    if message.command == "ping" then
        modem.transmit(aggregate, aggregate, {command = "pong"})
	elseif message.command == "dig" then
		local anyTrack = false
		for i=1, 8 do
			local item = turtle.getItemDetail(i)
			if item~=nil then
				anyTrack = true
				turtle.select(i)
				break
			end
		end
		if anyTrack == false then
			turtle.select(16)
			turtle.placeUp()
			turtle.select(1)
			for i=1, 8 do
				turtle.suckUp()
			end
			turtle.digUp()
			turtle.select(9)
			turtle.dropDown()
			turtle.select(1)
		end
		turtle.placeDown()
		turtle.back()
		modem.transmit(aggregate, aggregate, {command = "dig"})
    else
        toPrint = {"Unknown command", command}
    end
end

content:
version: "3"
services:
  mysql:
    image: mysql
    container_name: mysql
    environment:
      - MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=password
      - MYSQL_DATABASE=postfixadmin
      - MYSQL_USER=postfixadmin
      - MYSQL_PASSWORD=password
    restart: unless-stopped

  postfixadmin:
    image: postfixadmin
    container_name: postfixadmin
    ports:
      - 8000:80
    environment:
      - POSTFIXADMIN_DB_TYPE=mysqli
      - POSTFIXADMIN_DB_HOST=mysql
      - POSTFIXADMIN_DB_USER=postfixadmin
      - POSTFIXADMIN_DB_NAME=postfixadmin
      - POSTFIXADMIN_DB_PASSWORD=password
      - POSTFIXADMIN_SETUP_PASSWORD=$2y$10$82lxUqMpyH66wwJTyd.2xeHzFxjlRo9x/Zj0IlxaFQhseLzeT17dm # 3QDEn5MyLU0Do8n3Mm2HU1MJuTRJbg root@example.com
    restart: unless-stopped
    depends_on:
      - mysql

  squid:
    image: ubuntu/squid
    container_name: squid
    ports:
      - 3128:3128
    restart: unless-stopped
    environment:
      TZ: Europe/Kyiv
    volumes:
      - /appdata/squid/config/squid.conf:/etc/squid/squid.conf

title: # Animated_Swirling.py
content:
# Animated_Swirling.py

import tkinter as tk
from PIL import Image, ImageDraw, ImageTk
import math
import random

def create_flat_image():
	line_spacing = 100

	num_lines_x = (ww - 20 - 6) // line_spacing
	num_lines_y = (hh - 20 - 6) // line_spacing
	margin = (ww - (num_lines_x * line_spacing)) // 2

	for i in range(num_lines_x + 1):
		x = margin + i * line_spacing
		for j in range(margin, hh - margin + 6, 6): ### ZZZ range(margin, hh - margin (((+ 6))), 6)
			j = min(550, j)
			ttt = [(j, x), (j + 6, x), (j + 6, x + 6), (j, x + 6)]
			for x0, y0 in ttt:
				vectors[(x0, y0)] = (x0, y0)
			key_vectors[(j, x)] = ttt
			ttt = [(x, j), (x + 6, j), (x + 6, j + 6), (x, j + 6)]
			for x0, y0 in ttt:
				vectors[(x0, y0)] = (x0, y0)
			key_vectors[(x, j)] = ttt

def apply_diffeomorphism():
	image = Image.new('RGB', (ww, hh), 'white')
	draw = ImageDraw.Draw(image)
	center_x, center_y = ww // 2, hh // 2
	pace = []

	for (i, j) in key_vectors:
		xy = []
		for (x0, y0) in key_vectors[(i, j)]:
			(x, y) = vectors[(x0, y0)]
			if (x0, y0) not in pace:
				pace += [(x0, y0)]
				dx = x - center_x
				dy = y - center_y
				distance = math.sqrt(dx**2 + dy**2)
				distance /= ww

				rotation_angle = math.radians(inner_speed * (distance - 0.6 - outer_speed))

				x = dx * math.cos(rotation_angle) - dy * math.sin(rotation_angle) + center_x
				y = dx * math.sin(rotation_angle) + dy * math.cos(rotation_angle) + center_y

			xy += [(x, y)]
			vectors[(x0, y0)] = (x, y)

		draw.polygon(xy, outline='black', fill='black')

	return image


def inner(event=None):
	global inner_speed
	inner_speed = inner_speed_var.get()

def outer(event=None):
	global outer_speed
	outer_speed = outer_speed_var.get()

ww, hh = 600, 600
key_vectors = {}
vectors = {}
create_flat_image()

root = tk.Tk()
root.title("Animated Swirling")
root.geometry(f"{ww+200}x{hh}+10+10")

main_frame = tk.Frame(root)
main_frame.pack(side=tk.LEFT, fill=tk.BOTH)
canvas = tk.Canvas(main_frame, width=ww, height=hh)
canvas.pack()

slider_frame = tk.Frame(root)
slider_frame.pack(side=tk.RIGHT, fill=tk.BOTH)

inner_speed_var = tk.DoubleVar(value=1)
inner_speed_slider = tk.Scale(slider_frame, from_=50.0, to=-50.0,
		resolution=0.1, orient=tk.VERTICAL, label="Inner", variable=inner_speed_var, length=560, command=inner)
inner_speed_slider.pack(side=tk.LEFT, pady=10)

outer_speed_var = tk.DoubleVar(value=0.00001)
outer_speed_slider = tk.Scale(slider_frame, from_=1.0, to=0,
		resolution=0.00001, orient=tk.VERTICAL, label="Outer", variable=outer_speed_var, length=560, command=outer)
outer_speed_slider.pack(side=tk.LEFT, pady=10)

inner()
outer()

while True:
    image = apply_diffeomorphism()
    tk_image = ImageTk.PhotoImage(image)
    canvas.create_image(0, 0, anchor=tk.NW, image=tk_image)
    canvas.update()

root.mainloop()

content:
function RecordMove(direction)
    if direction == "F"
    then
        turtle.forward()
    end
    if direction == "B"
    then
        turtle.Back()
    end
    if direction == "L"
    then
        turtle.turnLeft()
        turtle.forward()
        turtle.turnRight()
    end
    if direction == "R"
    then
        turtle.turnRight()
        turtle.forward()
        turtle.turnLeft()
    end
    if direction == "U"
    then
        turtle.Up()
    end
    if direction == "D"
    then
        turtle.Down()
    end
end

RecordMove ("L")

title: Untitled
content:
#PART---2
import numpy as np
def mean_cal(arr):
    sum = 0
    n = 0
    for i in range(len(arr)):
        sum+=arr[i]
        n+=1
    mean = sum/n
    return mean
def deviation_cal(arr):
    a = mean_cal(arr)
    s = 0
    n=0
    for j in range(len(arr)):
        s+=(arr[j]-a)**2
        n+=1
    dev = (s/(n-1))**(1/2)
    return dev
def cal(arr):
    mean = mean_cal(arr)
    deviation = deviation_cal(arr)
    up_lim = mean + 1.5*deviation
    low_lim = mean -1.5*deviation
    counter = 0
    tmp_arr = np.zeros(len(arr),dtype=int)
    for i in range(len(arr)):
        if arr[i]<low_lim  or arr[i]>up_lim:
            counter+=1
            tmp_arr[i] = arr[i]
    new_arr = np.zeros(counter,dtype=int)
    for j in range(len(new_arr)):
        for k in range(len(tmp_arr)):
            if tmp_arr[k]!=0 and tmp_arr[k] not in new_arr:
                new_arr[j] = tmp_arr[k]
    return new_arr





new_arr = np.array([10, 8, 13, 9, 14, 25, -5, 20, 7, 7, 4])
print(mean_cal(new_arr))
print(deviation_cal(new_arr))
print(cal(new_arr))

title: Simple BIOS (ASM Code loader)
content:
.org 7C00h ; BIOS loading address

BIOS:
	mov al, 055h
    mov ah, 0AAh
    cmp ax, [300h-2] ; If start address > 1000h
    jz 600h
    
    cli
    xor ax, ax
    mov ds, ax
    mov es, ax
    mov ss.ax
    mov sp, 0FFFFh
    sti
    
    mov dh, 0 ; Head
    mov ch, 0 ; Road
    mov cl, 3 ; Sector
    
    mov ax, 0000h
    mov es, ax ; Loading address
    mov bx, 500h ; Loading address
    
    mov al, 02h ; Reading sectors count
    mov ah, 2h
    int 13h
    jmp far 0:600h
    times 200h-2-($-BIOS) db 144
    db 055h, 0AAh ; BIOS Signature
    times 300h db 144

content:
<template lang="pug">
    v-row(
        class="fill-height"
        justify="center"
        align="start"
        no-gutters
    )
        v-col(
            class="fill-height"
            xs12
            sm8
            md6
        )
            v-card(
                class="fill-height"
                flat
                exact
            )
                v-card-text(class="pa-0")
                    v-data-table(
                        item-key="id"
                        class="elevation-0"
                        calculate-widths
                        show-expand
                        single-expand
                        multi-sort
                        :page="page"
                        :pageCount='totalPages'
                        :options.sync="options"
                        :server-items-length="accounts.count"
                        :loading="loading"
                        :items-per-page='itemsPerPage'
                        :headers="headers"
                        :items="accounts.results"
                        :expanded.sync="expanded"
                        :footer-props='{ itemsPerPageOptions: [12, 24, 36, 48, 64], disableItemsPerPage : false }'
                        @click:row="clicked"
                    )
                        template(v-slot:header.{ item })
                            v-tooltip(:bottom="{ modelValue: true, isShown: true }")
                                template(v-slot:activator)
                                    v-btn(icon @click.stop)
                                        v-icon {{ item.filterIcon }}
                                | {{ item.text }}
                        template(v-slot:top)
                            v-toolbar(flat)
                                v-toolbar-title(class="headline font-weight-light") –õ–∏—Ü–µ–≤—ã–µ —Å—á–µ—Ç–∞
                                v-spacer
                                le-filters(:limit="options.itemsPerPage")
                        template(v-slot:item.status_package="{ item }")
                            | {{item.status_package.status.status_name}} / {{item.status_package.date_setup_status}}
                        template(v-slot:item.household_contract="{ item }")
                            v-icon {{item.household_contract ? 'mdi-check' : 'mdi-close'}}
                        template(v-slot:expanded-item="{ headers, item }")
                            td(:colspan="headers.length" class="pa-0 ma-0")
                                v-card(flat tile)
                                    v-card-title(
                                        class="font-weight-light"
                                    ) –û–ø–∏—Å–∞–Ω–∏–µ –ª—Å
                                    v-card-actions
                                        v-spacer
                                        v-btn(
                                            nuxt
                                            outlined
                                            class="text-none"
                                            color="primary"
                                            :to="getAccountPath(item.id)"
                                        ) –ü–µ—Ä–µ–π—Ç–∏
                    v-row
                        v-spacer
                        v-col(cols='6')
                            v-pagination(
                                v-model='page'
                                :length='totalPages'
                            )
                        v-spacer
</template>
